Package edu.ntnu.idatt1002.baecon.data

Class Entry

java.lang.Object
edu.ntnu.idatt1002.baecon.data.Entry
Direct Known Subclasses:
AccountingEntry, BudgetEntry
public abstract class Entry extends Object
Class representing an entry. An entry can be either an accounting entry or a budget entry.
